structure.unit: SCHOOL EMPLOYEES -- TEACHERS' RETIREMENT AND TENURE

law.history: Repealed 1990 Ky. Acts ch. 476, Pt. VI, sec. 616, effective July 13, 1990. -- Amended 1985 (1st Extra. Sess.) Ky. Acts ch. 10, sec. 21, effective October 18, 1985. -- Created 1984 Ky. Acts ch. 397, sec. 2, effective July 13, 1984.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Career-ladder commission to develop pilot program -- Commission report required -- Initiation of two-year program.
